### ===== KHANZA API TEST FILE =====
### REST Client Extension for VS Code
### Install: REST Client by Huachao Mao
### Usage: Click "Send Request" above each request block

### ===== ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES =====
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@contentType = application/json

### ===== ICD-10 TESTS =====

### 1. Search ICD-10 by keyword
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/10?search=hypertension&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 2. Get ICD-10 Detail by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/10/I10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 3. Get Recap ICD-10 by Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/recap/10?from=2024-01-01&until=2024-12-31&status_rawat=Selesai
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ===== ICD-9 TESTS =====

### 4. Search ICD-9 by keyword
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/9?search=diabetes&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 5. Get ICD-9 Detail by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/9/250.00
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 6. Get Most Used ICD-9 Codes (NEW) - Date Range Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/recap/9?from=2024-01-01&until=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 7. Get Most Used ICD-9 Codes - With Custom Limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/recap/9?from=2024-01-01&until=2024-12-31&limit=25
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 8. Get Most Used ICD-9 Codes - Short Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/recap/9?from=2024-06-01&until=2024-06-30&limit=15
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ===== ERROR TEST CASES =====

### 9. Missing Required Parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/recap/9
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 10. Missing From Parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/recap/9?until=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 11. Missing Until Parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/recap/9?from=2024-01-01
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 12. Invalid Date Format
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/recap/9?from=01-01-2024&until=31-12-2024
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 13. Limit Exceeds Maximum
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/recap/9?from=2024-01-01&until=2024-12-31&limit=200
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ===== BATCH TESTS FOR DIFFERENT PERIODS =====

### 14. Year 2024 - Q1
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/recap/9?from=2024-01-01&until=2024-03-31&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 15. Year 2024 - Q2
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/recap/9?from=2024-04-01&until=2024-06-30&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 16. Year 2024 - Q3
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/recap/9?from=2024-07-01&until=2024-09-30&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 17. Year 2024 - Q4
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/recap/9?from=2024-10-01&until=2024-12-31&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 18. Last 30 Days (Adjust dates as needed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/icd/recap/9?from=2024-11-19&until=2024-12-19&limit=15
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ===== NOTES FOR TESTING =====
###
### Before running tests:
### 1. Update @token with your actual JWT token
### 2. Ensure server is running on port 3000
### 3. Update @baseUrl if server is on different host/port
###
### How to get JWT Token:
### - Login to your Khanza system
### - Copy Authorization header value (everything after "Bearer ")
### - Paste into @token variable
###
### Response Status Codes:
### - 200: Success
### - 422: Missing/Invalid parameters
### - 401: Unauthorized (invalid token)
### - 404: Not found
### - 500: Server error
###
### Tips:
### - Click "Send Request" link above each request
### - Response appears in right panel
### - Use Ctrl+Alt+R to send last request again
### - Results are saved in response history
###
